  "data": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p>Starting at 1st level, your existence in a twilight state between life and death makes you difficult to defeat. When damage reduces you to 0 hit points, you can make a <strong>Charisma saving throw</strong> (DC 5 + the damage taken). On a success, you instead drop to 1 hit point. You can't use this feature if you are reduced to 0 hit points by <strong>radiant damage</strong> or by a <strong>critical hit</strong>.</p>\n<p>After the saving throw succeeds, you can't use this feature again until you finish a <strong>long rest</strong>.</p>",
